Data sources:

6502.svg, 6502Node.svg, pullups.js: Barry Silverman (derived from polygon data)
dep: Segher Boessenkool (list of probable additional depletion transistors)

notes on chip scale:

slide 20 in SIGGRAPH presentation:
  ~820 pixels per inch, derived from pin spacing of 0.1" and 0.6"
  results in a 6502 die size of 3.28 mm by 3.66 mm

high-res 6502 photos:
  about 0.73 microns per pixel

bitmap scale:
  about 0.94 microns per pixel
